how to create ebs volume and laucnch the instance and attach the ebs volume 

aws ec2 create-volume --availability-zone <availability-zone> --size <size-in-gb> --volume-type <volume-type>

aws ec2 run-instances --image-id <image-id> --instance-type <instance-type> --key-name <key-pair-name> --security-group-ids <security-group-ids> --subnet-id <subnet-id>



